PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Supply and Services of Gary Davidge, of Edmonton, Alberta, as a director of the Board of Directors of the Royal Canadian Mint to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, in the place of John D. Rooke, who has resigned.
